[FILE:211:descriptions/desc.single]
Dave Crossland's Cantarell is a contemporary Humanist sans serif that fully
support the following writing systems: Basic Latin, Western European,
Catalan, Baltic, Turkish, Central European, Dutch and Afrikaans.


